"TestLabelConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n155: \n156: - [ ] **T8.6** Test annotation constants\n157:   - Verify: `grep -q \"TestAnnotationConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n158: \n159: - [ ] **T8.7** Test condition type constants\n160:   - Verify: `grep -q \"TestConditionTypeConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n161: \n162: - [ ] **T8.8** Test condition reason constants\n163:   - Verify: `grep -q \"TestConditionReasonConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n164: \n165: - [ ] **T8.9** Test default value constants\n166:   - Verify: `grep -q \"TestDefaultConstants\" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n167: \n168: ### Phase 9: Validation & Quality\n169: \n170: - [ ] **T9.1** Verify JSON tags use camelCase\n171:   - Verify: `grep -E 'json:\"[a-z]' pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`\n172: \n173: - [ ] **T9.2** Verify godoc comments present for all constants\n174:   - Verify: `grep -c \"// \" pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go | grep -q \"[0-9]\"`\n175: \n176: - [ ] **T9.3** Verify `go build` succeeds\n177:   - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n178: \n179: - [ ] **T9.4** Verify `go test` passes\n180:   - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n181: \n182: - [ ] **T9.5** Verify `go vet` passes\n183:   - Verify: `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n184: \n185: ---\n186: \n187: ## Task Dependencies\n188: \n189: ```\n190: T1.1 → T1.2 → T1.3 [DONE]\n191:            ↓\n192: T2.1 → T2.2 → T2.3 → T2.4 → T2.5\n193:            ↓\n194: T3.1 → T3.2 → T3.3 → T3.4 → T3.5\n195:            ↓\n196: T4.1 → T4.2 → T4.3 → T4.4 → T4.5\n197:            ↓\n198: T5.1 → T5.2\n199:            ↓\n200: T6.1 → T6.2 → T6.3 → T6.4 → T6.5 → T6.6\n201:            ↓\n202: T7.1 [DONE]\n203:            ↓\n204: T8.1 → T8.2 → T8.3 → T8.4 [DONE]\n205:            ↓\n206: T8.5 → T8.6 → T8.7 → T8.8 → T8.9\n207:            ↓\n208: T9.1 → T9.2 → T9.3 → T9.4 → T9.5\n209: ```\n210: \n211: ---